To install the Rohingya Hanifi keyboard layout for Mac:

1. Download rhg-hanifi.dmg and double-click on it.

2. Drag rhg-hanifi.bundle to the "Drag here to install" directory.

3. Go to System Preferences and click "Keyboard."

4. Navigate to the "Input Sources" tab.

5. Click the plus button.

6. Find "rhg" in the list of languages.

7. Select the "Hanifi Rohingya" keyboard.

You should now be able to switch to the Hanifi Rohingya keyboard layout.
